    <item>
      <title>联合国在的黎波里举行会谈以解决利比亚中央银行危机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/un-holds-talks-in-tripoli-to-resolve-libya-s-central-bank-crisis</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联合国称，周一举行了利比亚敌对政府之间的会谈，试图解决该国央行危机，该危机已引发利比亚对石油生产和出口的封锁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/un-holds-talks-in-tripoli-to-resolve-libya-s-central-bank-crisis</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 05:17:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中美气候谈判将于周三在北京恢复</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/china-us-climate-talks-to-resume-from-wednesday-in-beijing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国和中国气候谈判代表将于周三在北京就深化减排和过渡资金问题恢复会谈，这两个污染最大的国家希望在 11 月的联合国全球峰会之前就关键问题达成协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/china-us-climate-talks-to-resume-from-wednesday-in-beijing</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 05:11:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国新总理将继续实行现金发放政策并于周二确定内阁名单</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/new-thai-pm-to-keep-cash-handout-finalize-cabinet-on-tuesday</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国新任领导人帕东丹·西那瓦重申了她将保留其政党备受争议的计划的承诺，即向几乎所有泰国成年人每人发放 10,000 泰铢（292 美元），并表示她的内阁阵容已经准备就绪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/new-thai-pm-to-keep-cash-handout-finalize-cabinet-on-tuesday</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 05:10:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波兰考虑改善国有企业治理，避免出售资产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/poland-eyes-governance-boost-for-state-firms-shuns-asset-sales</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在上一届民族主义政府大幅提升了国家在经济中的地位后，波兰政府没有计划将任何主要资产重新出售给私人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/poland-eyes-governance-boost-for-state-firms-shuns-asset-sales</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 05:02:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>普京投入巨资按照自己的形象塑造俄罗斯年轻人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/putin-is-spending-big-to-shape-russia-s-youth-in-his-own-image</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在俄罗斯，25 岁​​以下的年轻人中，除了弗拉基米尔·普京，没有其他人是他们的领导人。克里姆林宫决心确保新一代领导人继续以总统的形象为榜样。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/putin-is-spending-big-to-shape-russia-s-youth-in-his-own-image</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>蒙古总统不顾要求逮捕普京的呼声，迎接普京</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/putin-set-to-meet-top-mongolian-leaders-despite-calls-for-arrest</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管有人呼吁根据国际刑事法院有关战争罪的指控逮捕俄罗斯领导人弗拉基米尔·普京，但到访的俄罗斯领导人普京仍受到蒙古总统的热情接待。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/putin-set-to-meet-top-mongolian-leaders-despite-calls-for-arrest</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 03:11:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>习近平希望从非洲债务交易中获得更多回报、减少麻烦</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-09-02/china-africa-summit-xi-changes-terms-of-belt-and-road-initiative</link>
      <description><![CDATA[十年来，中国贷款激增，导致非洲国家陷入违约，如今北京提出了一项新建议：为中国提供可带来更好回报的商业贷款]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-09-02/china-africa-summit-xi-changes-terms-of-belt-and-road-initiative</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 23:00:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国暂停向以色列发放部分武器许可证 因存在违反加沙人道主义法的风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/uk-suspends-30-arms-licenses-to-israel-citing-risk-of-law-breach</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国首相基尔·斯塔默领导的新工党政府与盟友决裂，因为英国认为在加沙使用英国武器可能违反国际人道主义法，因此暂停了对以色列的部分武器许可。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/uk-suspends-30-arms-licenses-to-israel-citing-risk-of-law-breach</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 16:08:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>林宣布日本领导人竞选名单增至四位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/who-could-replace-kishida-candidates-who-could-be-japan-s-new-prime-minister</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本政府首席发言人表示，如果他成为国家领导人，将推行“亲民政治”，这使得本月自民党总裁选举的候选人名单增至四人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/who-could-replace-kishida-candidates-who-could-be-japan-s-new-prime-minister</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 02:41:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
